These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, ivory, grey, blood-red, red
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, trike, train, taxi
There 5 different types of food: spinach, raspberry, cucumber, pear, garlic
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, surfing, cricket, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person who likes grey is the person who likes grey##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
11. the person who likes red is between the person eating raspberry and the person driving the taxi##2
12. the person eating pear is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Color      | white        | ivory | red     | grey   | blood-red |
| Transport   | trike     | quad-bike      | train | taxi   | bike    |
| Food   | pear  | raspberry     | spinach | cucumber | garlic  |
| Sport           | rowing | surfing      | badminton     | cricket   | climbing     |

