.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, january, february, june, may
5 different games are played: go, backgammon, bridge, whist, chess
The people have 5 different jobs:  software-developer, project-manager, coach, teacher, librarian
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, sunflower, rose, daffodil
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the project-manager##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is between the software-developer and the person playing chess##2
 6. the person who growsrose is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the coach is the person playing whist##1
 9. the coach is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the coach is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | june | april | may    | january  | february    |
| Game   | chess    | backgammon       | bridge      | go | whist        |
| Job   | librarian   | project-manager     | software-developer    | teacher  | coach     |
| Flower     | sunflower    | bellflower | daffodil | rose | orchid |

