.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, november, october, may, july
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, accountant, designer, bartender, analyst
5 different games are played: chess, canasta, backgammon, domino, poker
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, siglo, game, alhambra, bluemaster
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing canasta##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 4. the dressmaker is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 8. the dressmaker is on the right of the accountant##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is the bartender##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person playing poker##1
13. the bluemaster-smoker is between the analyst and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Birthday         | april | july     | october   | november   | may |
| Job   | analyst  | accountant | dressmaker | bartender | designer        |
| Game   | backgammon      | canasta      | domino       | poker       | chess       |
| Cigar         | siglo | bluemaster  | alhambra    | dunhill    | game        |

