.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, trike, tram, train
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, soccer, skiing, badminton, basketball
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, june, may, december, january
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, soy-milk, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
 1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person driving the tram##2
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Transport          | train  | trike     | tram   | motorbike     | bus |
| Sport         | basketball | skateboarding    | skiing  | badminton | soccer   |
| Birthday   | june        | august    | january     | may     | december    |
| Beverage   | cola    | soy-milk | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | almond-milk   |

