.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, february, march, august, september
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, camping, puzzles, cooking, collecting
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller, mystery, musical, fantasy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, electronic, classical, pop
 1. the fan r&b is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan classical##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan electronic##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan electronic##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Birthday   | august       | september       | december   | march      | february    |
| Hobby       | collecting | cooking        | singing       | puzzles       | camping |
