 7. the engineer is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the writer is on the far right##1
11. the modern house is between the tower house and the designer##2
12. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the tower house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
