 1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person watching western movies is between the person drinking cola and the fan hip-hop##2
 5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 7. the fan funk is on the right of the fan folk##1
 8. the fan country is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is the fan funk##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the fan folk##1
12. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the left of the fan country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
