 7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the trike##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person driving the boat is between the person drinking sprite and the person eating pumpkin##2
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
13. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
