.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, bridge, mah-jongg, whist
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, february, september, june, march
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, thriller, sports, animation, superhero
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, rose, aconite, orchid
 1. the person watching superhero movies is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person watching thriller movies##2
 2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsrose is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's birthday is in september##2
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
13. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Game    | bridge       | mah-jongg    | whist | snooker  | monopoly        |
| Birthday       | march | july | september  | june | february    |
| Movie-Genre       | sports        | animation   | thriller  | superhero   | family |
| Flower   | aconite       | rose      | orchid      | dahlia | amaryllis  |

