.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different games are played: whist, chess, snooker, poker, backgammon
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, game, dannemann, swisher, bongani
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, card-games, hiking, woodworking
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, pepper, spinach, pomegranate, cranberry
 1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the dannemann-smoker##2
 3. the person playing poker is the swisher-smoker##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
 6. the person playing poker is between the bongani-smoker and the person eating pepper##2
 7. the person eating pomegranate is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person playing whist is the person eating spinach##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the dannemann-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
13. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Game      | whist      | chess         | poker      | snooker | backgammon     |
| Cigar           | game | dannemann | swisher | bongani    | baccarat  |
| Hobby   | hiking  | drawing    | cooking | card-games    | woodworking |
| Food   | spinach  | pepper        | artichoke   | pomegranate    | cranberry     |

